name: TradeWix
public_notice: TradeWix (WIX) has migrated from their older BSC contract to a new one on ETH. For more information, please visit their website.

description.en:
TradeWix is the next generation of crypto security 3.0

No need for honeypot checker or tokensniffer, we combine any kind of check up in one. 
Our TradeWix-Trust-Rate-Score is the most accurate check up that you can find out there!
We provide a trustworthy KYC & AUDIT and combine everything with our ecosystem.

- Team is doxxed
- App is LIVE on Android / iOS soon
- App integrated launchpad
- Revolutionairy ecosystem
- 10k NFTs LIVE
- NFT & Token staking
- Privat Sales for upcoming projects
